<P>
Game Story 
</P>
</TYPE>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA050290-0023 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 212633 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
May 2, 1990, Wednesday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Sports; Part C; Page 1; Column 4; Sports Desk 
</P>
