BETTING WITH BOB 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Times handicapper Bob Mieszerski, who has seen his bankroll shrink from $1,000 
to $814 after the first week of the Hollywood Park meeting, will try to turn 
things around today when he wagers $10 daily doubles from Dandy Bear, Exploded 
Jr. and Lucky Street in the first to Stone House in the second. 
</P>
