<P>
NIBBLES AND BITS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
Compiled by Kenneth Williams 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
More than 100 works by Orange County artists will be auctioned off Saturday 
evening when the Arts Associates of Huntington Beach sponsor a fund-raiser, 
"Portfolio '90," at the Huntington Beach Civic Center, 2000 Main St., from 6 to 
10:30 p.m. There will be live entertainment, a Champagne buffet supper donated 
by local restaurants, and a ceremony at which "visual artist of the year," 
"performing artist of the year" and "volunteer service to the arts" awards will 
be presented by Mayor Tom Mays. Donor tickets are $25 per person and Patron 
tickets are $125 per couple. 
</P>
<P>
Proceeds will benefit numerous arts programs in the city including a 
scholarship program, children's workshops, annual juried exhibitions, Arts on 
the Green and the Family Concert Series. Reservations: Caroline Browning at 
(714) 846-2855. Information: The Arts Associates at (714) 842-9185. 
</P>
