<P>
Photo, Orned (Chicken) Gabriel; Photo, SAN DIEGO AT LARGE: Orned (Chicken) 
Gabriel had his 15 minutes of fame in April, 1988, when he exposed the "Rambo 
Squad" of deputies at the El Cajon jail. Now he's trying to rebuild his life 
and stay out of trouble. 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
