L.A.'s MacArthur Park turned violent. Members of the Revolutionary Communist 
Party and Revolutionary Communist Youth Brigade clashed with riot-clad 
officers. One marked detainee's name on shirt, above. ; Photo, Police officers 
close in on a May Day protester who held them at bay with a tar can. ROBERT 
DURELL / Los Angeles Times; Photo, Police take two protesters into custody in 
MacArthur Park. They arrested 15 people. MIKE MULLEN / For The Times 
</P>
