being sold to a Japanese firm. ; Photo, Northrop in Anaheim: Orange County's 
oldest aerospace plant will be demolished over the next year at a cost of $3 
million. The 53-acre facitlity has grown over the years to more than 600,000 
square feet. 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
