REDEVELOPMENT; LAND USE; DEFENSE INDUSTRY -- ORANGE COUNTY; ORANGE COUNTY -- 
HISTORY; DEMOLITION; AEROSPACE INDUSTRY -- ORANGE COUNTY; ORANGE COUNTY -- 
