<TEXT>
<P>
PacBell Expo: Pacific Bell will host its fourth annual TEXPO telecommunications 
conference and exhibition today through Friday at the Anaheim Convention 
Center. 
</P>
<P>
The exhibits of futuristic telecommunications applications will include an 
electronic library, high-definition television and shopping by computer. 
</P>
