<TEXT>
<P>
Whirlpool Corp. said today that it is combining several units into one 
subsidiary that will handle marketing outside North America and Europe. 
</P>
<P>
The new unit, Whirlpool Overseas Corp., will combine the company's Benton 
Harbor-based export sales group with its overseas business group in Comerio, 
Italy. It will also include four wholly owned sales companies in Taiwan, Hong 
Kong, Thailand and Australia, the company said. 
